.DT
inside_the_short
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
inside_the_short

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
inside_the_short -  This method produces the inside messages for the given object up to the player object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string inside_the_short(object ob,
object play)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object to generate the short for
%^BOLD%^play%^RESET%^ - the player to generate the short up to
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/secure/simul_efun/inside_shorts.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method produces the inside messages for the given object up
to the player object.  This one generates 'the_short' messages.
This should only be called with an object that is a container.
It will produce weird and incorrect messages otherwise.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
inside_a_short()

.EP

